---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Payroll Services for California Small Businesses — Pink Payroll">

  <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
  <section class="bg-brand-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 text-center">
      <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-5">Payroll Services</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-6 leading-tight">
        The Precision of a Powerhouse.<br class="hidden md:block" />
        <span class="text-pink">The Service of a Boutique Agency.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
        Full-service payroll and tax filing for California small businesses — where every account is personally overseen by a senior expert, not handed off to a call center.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-pink text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-pink-dark transition-colors text-base">
          Get a Payroll Quote
        </a>
        <a href="/switching" class="border-2 border-white/40 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:border-white hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors text-base">
          See How Switching Works
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== THE PROBLEM ===== -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Sound Familiar?</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-black">Tired of Being Just a Ticket Number?</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

      <!-- Big Box Pain -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-8">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-5">The Big Box Experience</p>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          {[
            'You call and get a different rep every time — one who has never seen your account.',
            'Simple questions take days to resolve through a ticket queue.',
            'Errors surface at tax time, not when they happen.',
            'You\'re paying enterprise pricing for entry-level service.',
            'They automated your account. You became a number.',
          ].map((item) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-brand-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-300 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/>
              </svg>
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xs text-gray-400 italic border-t border-gray-200 pt-4">
          "I thought I'd go with one of those 'big' payroll companies… big mistake. I was right back with Pink Payroll as soon as I could get away from them."
          <span class="block font-semibold mt-1 not-italic">— San Diego Business Owner</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pink Payroll Solution -->
      <div class="bg-pink/5 border border-pink/20 rounded-2xl p-8">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-pink mb-5">The Pink Payroll Difference</p>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          {[
            'A dedicated, US-based team that knows your business by name — not by ticket.',
            'Every account is personally overseen by a senior payroll expert.',
            'Questions answered accurately, fast — not routed through a queue.',
            'Proactive compliance monitoring, so problems are caught before they cost you.',
            'Boutique attention with enterprise-grade systems backing every payroll run.',
          ].map((item) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-brand-black text-sm leading-relaxed">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-pink flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xs text-brand-gray italic border-t border-pink/20 pt-4">
          "Pink payroll is top notch. There are times when I go to their team for general questions over my own accountant."
          <span class="block font-semibold mt-1 not-italic">— San Diego Business Owner, Client since 2014</span>
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== FULL-SERVICE SOLUTION ===== -->
  <section class="bg-brand-light-gray/40 border-y border-brand-light-gray">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">What We Handle</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-4">Full-Service Payroll, Built Around Your Business</h2>
        <p class="text-brand-gray text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Every payroll run is audited by a human expert — not just a software algorithm. We catch discrepancies before they become compliance problems.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        {[
          { title: 'Payroll Processing', desc: 'Weekly, biweekly, semi-monthly, or monthly — we run payroll on your schedule, accurately, every time.' },
          { title: 'Payroll Tax Filing', desc: 'Federal and California state tax deposits and filings handled on your behalf. We track deadlines so you don\'t have to.' },
          { title: 'Direct Deposit', desc: 'Fast, reliable direct deposit for your entire team. Employees paid on time, every pay period.' },
          { title: 'New Hire Reporting', desc: 'California new hire reporting submitted automatically. Stay compliant from day one.' },
          { title: 'Year-End W-2 & 1099', desc: 'We prepare and file all year-end forms. Your employees and contractors receive accurate documents on time.' },
          { title: 'Compliance Monitoring', desc: 'California labor law is complex and constantly changing. We monitor updates so your payroll stays compliant.' },
          { title: 'Multi-State Payroll', desc: 'Employees in more than one state? We handle the complexity of multi-state payroll and tax obligations.' },
          { title: 'Amended Returns', desc: 'Tax amendments and corrections filed correctly — including 941 amendments that have saved our clients thousands.' },
          { title: 'HR & Benefits Integration', desc: 'Payroll that connects seamlessly with your HR, timekeeping, and workers\' comp policies.' },
        ].map(({ title, desc }) => (
          <div class="bg-white border border-brand-light-gray rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-pink mb-4"></div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-black mb-2">{title}</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">{desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== THE HUMAN DIFFERENCE ===== -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-center">

      <!-- Copy -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Our Team</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-6">
          Expert Oversight.<br />Not Call Center Roulette.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-gray text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Pink Payroll was founded on a single conviction: small businesses deserve the same caliber of payroll expertise as the Fortune 500 — without the impersonal, ticket-number treatment.
        </p>
        <p class="text-brand-gray text-base mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          <strong class="text-brand-black">Erica, our Founder & CEO,</strong> built this company around that standard. Every operational decision, service offering, and team member reflects her commitment to precision and personalized service.
        </p>
        <p class="text-brand-gray text-base mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          <strong class="text-brand-black">Laura and Sarah, our Senior Payroll Managers,</strong> personally oversee every client account. They lead a hand-picked, US-based support team trained to know your business — your industry, your pay schedule, your compliance needs — not just your account number.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-brand-light-gray/60 border border-brand-light-gray rounded-xl p-5">
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-black font-semibold mb-1">Our Promise</p>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Every Pink Payroll client is personally overseen by a senior expert and supported by a dedicated team that actually knows their business. You will never explain your situation from scratch to a stranger.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Stats / Trust Signals -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        {[
          { stat: '15+', label: 'Years serving California small businesses' },
          { stat: '5.0★', label: 'Average rating across 40+ verified reviews' },
          { stat: '100%', label: 'US-based payroll team — no offshore outsourcing' },
          { stat: '$0', label: 'Hidden fees. Transparent pricing, always.' },
        ].map(({ stat, label }) => (
          <div class="bg-white border border-brand-light-gray rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-pink mb-2">{stat}</p>
            <p class="text-brand-gray text-xs leading-snug">{label}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
        <div class="col-span-2">
          <a href="/contact" class="block w-full bg-pink text-white font-semibold text-center py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-pink-dark transition-colors">
            Get a Payroll Quote &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== SOCIAL PROOF ===== -->
  <section class="bg-brand-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">

      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-1 mb-4">
          {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#F3BD33]" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/>
            </svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-2">40+ Five-Star Reviews</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold">What California Business Owners Are Saying</h2>
      </div>

      <!-- 3 featured quotes -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5 mb-8">
        {[
          {
            quote: '"They make all my payments on time and keep great records. After COVID, they filed amended returns that saved me thousands of dollars. The whole staff is friendly and helpful!"',
            attr: 'San Diego Business Owner',
            source: 'Yelp, 2025',
          },
          {
            quote: '"Working with Pink Payroll was honestly such a breath of fresh air. After years with a horrible payroll company, I was scared to switch — but they were so patient and kind. I truly feel Pink Payroll wants their customers to be successful."',
            attr: 'San Diego Business Owner',
            source: 'Yelp, 2026',
          },
          {
            quote: '"I get approached by other payroll service providers on a fairly regular basis, and I always tell them I would not even consider changing providers. Their attention to detail and outstanding customer service is unmatched."',
            attr: 'President, Construction Company',
            source: 'Client since 2008',
          },
        ].map(({ quote, attr, source }) => (
          <figure class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-7 flex flex-col">
            <div class="flex gap-0.5 mb-4">
              {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
                <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#F3BD33]" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/>
                </svg>
              ))}
            </div>
            <blockquote class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-1 mb-5">{quote}</blockquote>
            <figcaption>
              <p class="text-white text-xs font-bold">{attr}</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">{source}</p>
            </figcaption>
          </figure>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- 2 more quotes, wider -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        {[
          {
            quote: '"Pink Payroll is a true local gem. As a restaurant owner, payroll is one of those things you need to be 100% accurate every single time. I\'ve been with Pink Payroll for over 5 years — they have never let me down."',
            attr: 'Restaurant Owner, San Diego',
            source: 'Google Review',
          },
          {
            quote: '"I have worked with multiple payroll companies over the years and no one comes close to the quality of service they provide. They go above and beyond — every single time."',
            attr: 'San Diego Business Owner',
            source: 'Google Review, 2025',
          },
        ].map(({ quote, attr, source }) => (
          <figure class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-7 flex flex-col">
            <div class="flex gap-0.5 mb-4">
              {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
                <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#F3BD33]" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/>
                </svg>
              ))}
            </div>
            <blockquote class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-1 mb-5">{quote}</blockquote>
            <figcaption>
              <p class="text-white text-xs font-bold">{attr}</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">{source}</p>
            </figcaption>
          </figure>
        ))}
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== FINAL CTA ===== -->
  <section class="bg-pink text-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 text-center">
      <p class="text-pink-light text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Ready to Switch?</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-5">We Make the Transition Easy.</h2>
      <p class="text-pink-light text-lg mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Our team has guided hundreds of businesses away from big-box payroll companies. We handle the setup, the data migration, and the compliance details — so you don't have to.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-white text-pink font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors text-base">
          Get a Payroll Quote
        </a>
        <a href="/switching" class="border-2 border-white/60 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:border-white hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors text-base">
          How Switching Works
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
